Introduction
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
The Gordon's blog is an example of a blog that will be used in Hoa's
documentation along chapters.


Usage
¯¯¯¯¯
We start PHP FastCGI:
    $ php-cgi -b 127.0.0.1:9000&
    or
    $ php-fpm -d listen=127.0.0.1:9000

Then, we start Bhoa to get a quick look of the application:
    $ Data/Bin/myapp bhoa --root hoa://Application/Public

Finally, go to http://127.0.0.1:8888 to view the Gordon's blog!


